    "body": "The LSP settings types for the [ZLS](https://github.com/zigtools/zls) language server were based of https://github.com/zigtools/zls-vscode which has been deprecated and contains mostly outdated config options. It has since been replaced by https://codeberg.org/ziglang/vscode-zig. ZLS offers a [schema.json](https://github.com/zigtools/zls/blob/master/schema.json) file to describe it's own `zls.json` config file that also matches LSP based configuration. This is beneficial over the `package.json` because it avoids the inclusion of config options that are specific the VS Code extension.\r\n\r\nBecause the schema file is primarily intended for standalone a `zls.json` config file, the properties are not prefixed with `zls.` which is why I had to add the `append_config_section` option.",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-27T22:30:12Z",
